{"tid":667294,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"多唔多人試過閃親腰？","createTime":"2018-05-16T15:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T16:30:40.000Z","uid":51740,"like":2,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"60f0ae70f435c50eaf17390c31024a5f33dcabf7","tid":667294,"uid":51740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"話說都成個半月前，<br />\n<br />\n果日咁啱瞓黎頸，成個背脊僵硬晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個唔覺意用力過猛就聽到條腰「啪」左一野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟手就行唔到要人扶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCheck左筋骨無事，淨係肌力拉傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後睇左幾次針灸，個幾星期跌打，腰就好返7788，係坐得耐起身會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而係pat pat 對落大脾位麻痺，跌打佬話係條肌肉未好返晒，壓住座骨神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但連續睇左個幾星期跌打都無晒起色咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人有類似經驗分享下，最好有跌打/醫生介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9f4f6ef1ab75dc0a41d5f0a8b966155e2690ad","tid":667294,"uid":173683,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"用扭親會唔會好啲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac6cc6ec4995589083ae6a38196045699bb9b0a","tid":667294,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b267eedcfbfc8d965bf6377de5dad6a9e50db7b0","tid":667294,"uid":156331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e8a5c64fd4d3248879a8300952011eebb1d43bf","tid":667294,"uid":156331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d9f3552e5ff84a9dca78f63b9bb77b00